rmal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaca7049bc1739d585a84e7abf3a6134ac865176","tid":2193020,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8778e4a93f21cdd0a2cfb9aac436b386774143e","tid":2193020,"uid":376052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:49:12.000Z","msg":"你問得都係想去架啦 咪去囉 冇壞嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:52:31.000Z","msg":"一半半, 喺黃店訂左檯咋, 未決定真係食唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9405303c96b5cd7cb3990c3eb96a75572e1a4e53","tid":2193020,"uid":310297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea37d36c6275ec759a040a408c98a85361c15211","tid":2193020,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T13:33:52.000Z","msg":"話說成十年前同ex開始一齊, 後來一齊住左幾年 <br />\n到四年前佢搬走左散埋, 我懶搬屋就繼續租嗰喥<br />\n<br />\n分手原因好多, 但主因都係我同佢屋企人極唔夾<br />\n佢屋企人係極傳統深藍嗰種, 見親都嘈交, 四年前嗰時嘈已有關顏色但唔係唯一原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢四年都仲有睇下對方FB/IG, 都知佢有男友<br />\n咁但散左一年後開始都耐唔耐(可能一兩個月)有Whatsapp傾幾句, 都知佢唔太鐘意佢男友但又仲一齊住緊<br />\n<br />\n咁我反正都慣左毒撚, 咁耐都冇乜feel, 都唔太理佢, 都成兩年冇見. 我都冇乜特別想拍拖, 可能預唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢前兩日佢主動約我下星期喺我哋紀念日約我食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁我係應承左, book埋檯<br />\n<br />\n究竟佢係咪玩九我？去唔去食飯好?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 飯點都要食咪當搵條女陪囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 玩鳩你咋唔好去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"記得保護返自己<br />\n車輪就盡量避喇<br />\n隔咁耐變化可以好大<br />\n小心為上"},{"pid":"db1d0f4ad545fc86f0c690fb406d62e6fec104a6","tid":2193020,"uid":279513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e56d3f5c6a9e8a4cf15c36c4d1ae2b40ab54dfea","tid":2193020,"uid":42625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d11523e808f80ab11ab5ef90ccffb7fcd362b32","tid":